<h1>Encode Your text</h1>

<p>Enter the phrase or sentence you would like to encode in the box below 
and select a letter to use as your Encryption Key.</p>
<p>Important: Please select a letter that is not in the message you want to encode</p>


<%= render 'encode_form' %>

<% if @encoded_text.present? %>
<div class="card my-5">
    <div class="card-body my-2">
      <p class='card-title fw-bold'>Here is your encoded text:</p>
      <p class='card-text fs-5'><%= @encoded_text %></p>
    </div>
  </div>
<% end %>

<p>Want to see how the decoding part works?</p>
<%= link_to "Decode", decode_xor_index_path, class:"btn btn-dark btn-lg" %>